# Backend base URL (no trailing slash).
# - Android emulator: can omit (defaults to http://10.0.2.2:3000) or set explicitly.
# - Physical phone (Expo Go / dev build): use your computer's LAN IP, e.g.:
#   EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.1.100:3000
# Do NOT use http://localhost:3000 on a real device — localhost is the phone itself.
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=
